{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01VW6yW3W6CzdmLED7EUYWeA","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package evolution\n     2→\n     3→import (\n     4→\t\"context\"\n     5→\n     6→\t\"github.com/cloche-dev/cloche/internal/domain\"\n     7→)\n     8→\n     9→// LLMClient abstracts LLM calls for evolution stages.\n    10→type LLMClient interface {\n    11→\tComplete(ctx context.Context, systemPrompt, userPrompt string) (string, error)\n    12→}\n    13→\n    14→// CollectedData is the input to the Classifier and Reflector.\n    15→type CollectedData struct {\n    16→\tRuns            []*domain.Run\n    17→\tCaptures        map[string][]*domain.StepExecution // run_id -> step executions\n    18→\tKnowledgeBase   string                             // contents of knowledge/<workflow>.jsonl\n    19→\tCurrentPrompts  map[string]string                  // relative path -> content\n    20→\tCurrentWorkflow string                             // .cloche file content\n    21→\tWorkflowPath    string                             // path to .cloche file\n    22→\tProjectDir      string\n    23→\tWorkflowName    string\n    24→}\n    25→\n    26→// Lesson is a structured insight extracted by the Reflector.\n    27→type Lesson struct {\n    28→\tID              string   `json:\"id\"`\n    29→\tCategory        string   `json:\"category\"`\n    30→\tStepType        string   `json:\"step_type,omitempty\"`\n    31→\tTarget          string   `json:\"target,omitempty\"`\n    32→\tInsight         string   `json:\"insight\"`\n    33→\tSuggestedAction string   `json:\"suggested_action\"`\n    34→\tEvidence        []string `json:\"evidence\"`\n    35→\tConfidence      string   `json:\"confidence\"`\n    36→}\n    37→\n    38→// EvolutionResult records what an evolution pass produced.\n    39→type EvolutionResult struct {\n    40→\tID             string   `json:\"id\"`\n    41→\tProjectDir     string   `json:\"project_dir\"`\n    42→\tWorkflowName   str